        <h3 class="f14">职位描述</h3>      
            <div class="cl">
                     
                    <p>
	&bull; Hardware Architect<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;Familiar with system architecture design include<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;System bandwidth calculation and performance evaluation<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;Key component selection and mini spec. creation and definition<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;Power budgeting<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;System level simulations include antenna, thermal, SI, audio<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;Familiar main stream mobile solutions like Nvidia, TI, MTK, SPRD etc&hellip;<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;Familiar with baseband design and RF subsystem (include WWAN and connectivity)<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;Familiar with the portfolios and roadmap as well as the technical trend of the key components in a mobile phone or tablet like power subsystem, display subsystem, IO subsystem (like CTP), camera, audio sub system, memory subsystem, sensor sub system<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;Familiar with system validations include both software and hardware<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;Familiar with tire one carrier engagement and TA experiences<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;&gt; 10years system or hardware team management experiences<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;&gt; 5 years System Architect experiences<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;Broad network in the mobile phone design industry, familiar with main stream vendor, OEMs, ODMs and IDHs<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;Familiar with the key component sourcing and pricing in mobile phone design<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;Familiar with operational tasks with ODMs and OEMs like NPI, DFM, RMA, etc&hellip;<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;Must have software development background and working experiences<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;Good at data analysis and data mining<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;Good communication skill sets good at leadership and convince<br />
	&radic; Good spoken and written English<br />
	&radic;&nbsp;BSEE is required, MSEE will be a plus</p>   
                   
